---
import BaseHead from '../components/BaseHead.astro'
import Header from '../components/Header.astro'
import Footer from '../components/Footer.astro'
import { SITE_TITLE, SITE_DESCRIPTION } from '../config'
---

<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <BaseHead title={SITE_TITLE} description={SITE_DESCRIPTION} />
  </head>
  <body>
    <Header title={SITE_TITLE} />
    <main>
      <div class="flow-root">
        <div class="float-left hidden md:block">
          <pre
            class="my-0 py-0 text-green-700">Welcome to Wanying's personal website! 😄</pre>
        </div>
        <div
          class="float-right rounded-full shadow-md shadow-neutral-600 mr-10"
        >
          <img class="rounded-full h-auto max-w-[120px]" src="/wanying.jpg" />
        </div>
      </div>
      <h2
        class="text-lg font-bold mb-6 underline underline-offset-8 decoration-4 decoration-orange-900"
      >
        Bio.
      </h2>
      <p>
        <a href="https://orcid.org/0000-0002-1392-1584">
        <strong>Wanying Ling (凌宛莹)</strong> <img style="display:inline; vertical-align:text-top;" alt="ORCID logo" src="/ORCIDiD_iconvector.svg" width="15" height="15" /></a>
        , aka Gufan (谷凡), is a PhD student in the Department of Sociology at the University of Hong Kong.
      </p>
      <p>
    My research interests intersect at the nexus of work and health, aging and the life course, and gender inequality, utilizing tools from formal demography and data science. I engage with multidisciplinary topics in social demography, social epidemiology, and public policy. My academic research is primarily focused on work-life inequalities in Asia and Europe. This focus has led me to explore several key areas: how work characteristics (such as quantity and quality) can either mitigate or exacerbate health inequalities among populations; the levels and trends in gender gaps in working life expectancy across various institutional settings; the impact of early work experiences on health later in life; and finally, the effect of health in later life on the working lives and well-being of intra-household members.
	</p>
	<p>
    My recent research interests include: working life expectancy; decomposition methods for life expectancies; tattooists and tattooing; qualitative comparative analysis and necessity comparative analysis.
      </p>
      <div class="hidden lg:block">
        <h2
          class="text-lg font-bold mb-6 underline underline-offset-8 decoration-4 decoration-orange-900"
        >
          Edu.
        </h2>
        <table class="table-auto shadow-none text-base">
          <tbody>
            <tr>
              <td>2023 - Present</td>
              <td><strong>Ph.D.</strong> in Sociology</td>
              <td>The University of Hong Kong</td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
              <td>2020 - 2023</td>
              <td><strong>M.Phil.</strong> in Demography</td>
              <td>Renmin University of China</td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
              <td>2016 - 2020</td>
              <td><strong>B.Sc.</strong> in Statistics (Minor in Sociology)</td>
              <td>Minzu University of China</td>
            </tr>
          </tbody>
        </table>
      </div>
      <h2
        class="mt-4 text-lg font-bold mb-6 underline underline-offset-8 decoration-4 decoration-orange-900"
      >
        Click.
      </h2>
      <button
        class="mx-1 text-sm rounded py-1 px-6 border border-transparent bg-gray-200 w-100 hover:bg-orange-900 hover:border-orange-900 hover:text-gray-100 transition ease-in-out duration-200"
        onclick="location.href='https://scholar.google.com/citations?user=1MBGTW0AAAAJ'"
        type="button">Google Scholar</button
      >
      <button
        class="mx-1 text-sm rounded py-1 px-6 border border-transparent bg-gray-200 w-100 hover:bg-orange-900 hover:border-orange-900 hover:text-gray-100 transition ease-in-out duration-200"
        onclick="location.href='https://twitter.com/LingWanying'"
        type="button">Twitter</button
      >
      <button
        class="mx-1 text-sm rounded py-1 px-6 border border-transparent bg-gray-200 w-100 hover:bg-orange-900 hover:border-orange-900 hover:text-gray-100 transition ease-in-out duration-200"
        onclick="location.href='https://github.com/wanyingling'"
        type="button">Github</button
      >
      <h2
        class="mt-8 text-lg font-bold mb-6 underline underline-offset-8 decoration-4 decoration-orange-900"
      >
        Contact.
      </h2>
      <ul class="list-disc px-4">
        <li>
          Email: <a href="mailto:lingwany@connect.hku.hk"
            >lingwany@connect.hku.hk</a
          >
        </li>
        <li>Address: 8.25, 8/F., The Jockey Club Tower, Pokfulam Road, Hong Kong SAR</li>
      </ul>
    </main>
    <br />
    <Footer />
  </body>
</html>
